La Commission de l'assurance-emploi du Canada
Veuillez ne pas répondre à ce courriel. Cette adresse courriel n'accepte pas les messages entrants.
Déclaration de confidentialité
Ce courriel est destiné uniquement à l'usage de la personne ou de l'entité à laquelle il est adressé. Si vous avez reçu ce courriel par erreur, veuillez le supprimer. Si ce courriel ne vous était pas destiné, toute utilisation, révision, retransmission, distribution, diffusion, copie, impression ou autre utilisation de ce courriel, ou toute autre mesure basée sur ce courriel, est strictement interdite. Votre coopération est appréciée.
Hello,
If you receive Employment Insurance (EI) benefits this year, you will need a T4E to file your taxes.
Use My Service Canada Account (MSCA) to access your T4E online instead of receiving a paper copy. It is faster, more secure, and better for the environment. By going paperless, you can avoid postal delays and get your T4E as early as February 1!

Canada Employment Insurance Commission
Please do not reply to this email. This email address does not accept incoming messages.
Privacy Statement
This e-mail is intended only for the use of the person or entity to whom it is addressed. In case you have received this email by mistake, please delete it. If this email was not intended for you, any use, revision, retransmission, distribution, dissemination, copying, printing or other use of this e-mail, or any other action based on this e-mail, is strictly prohibited. Thank you for your cooperation.
Hello,
If you receive Employment Insurance (EI) benefits this year, you will need a T4E to file your taxes.
Use My Service Canada Account (MSCA) to access your T4E online instead of receiving a paper copy. It's faster, more secure, and better for the environment. By going paperless, you can avoid postal delays and get your T4E as early as February 1!
